ine maleate','Biomed','Tab','أقراص','100mg','3','مضاد للإكتئاب','','6222001401165','',5852,'2024-10-21',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'Fluvoxamine is an antidepressant which functions pharmacologically as a selective serotonin reuptake inhibitor. Though it is in the same class as other SSRI drugs, it is most often used to treat obsessive-compulsive disorder.
